<div class="story"> <p>Georgetown Sands is an ocean front town house complex consisting of 9 buildings with 2 units in the oceanfront building and six units in each of the  other 8 buildings. There is an active home owners association and they collect an HOA fee which covers the costs of maintaining the exterior of the units, the private road and the pool and tennis courts. You can find Georgetown Sands just past <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/sand-dollar-shores.asp" title="Sand Dollar Shores">Sand Dollar Shores</a> and before you get to <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/sea-acres.asp" title="Sea Acres">Sea Acres</a>. </p>
